{{Quote|A sand-rat like you could never begin to match their price.|Han Solo, to [[Serji-X Arrogantus]]|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 8">[[Star Wars (1977) 8|''Star Wars'' (1977) 8]]</ref>}}
'''Sand-rats''' were a species of rodent found in deserts. They were the most common target of [[Jimm Doshun]]'s [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] prior to Jimm's joining the [[Star-Hoppers of Aduba-3|Sprites]]. Calling someone a sand-rat was considered an insult.<ref name="Supply Lines">{{TORcite|type=faction|Imperial|Supply Lines|Tatooine}}</ref>

Another species of sand-rat was found on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. Yet a third species of sand-rat was found on [[Jerne]].

